# Monitoring Framework (Enterprise AI)

## What to Monitor
- Quality: accuracy, precision/recall, hallucination rate (if LLM)
- Adoption: usage, task completion, override rate
- Trust: incident rate, escalation rate, complaint signals
- Drift: data drift, concept drift, prompt drift (if LLM)
- Ops: latency, uptime, throughput, cost

## Monitoring Cadence
- Daily: incidents, latency, cost anomalies
- Weekly: overrides, quality sampling, drift checks
- Monthly: stakeholder review + governance check-in
